 The first term represents the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

redistributive motive
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

: the desire to use the commodity tax to transfer money from the rich to
 the poor by subsidizing goods consumed by low earners.
 
