\begin_layout Subsubsection
Regression Results
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "tab:BiasEffects"

\end_inset

 presents estimates of Equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:BiasEffects"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 Column 1 is our primary specification.
 Paralleling the unconditional relationships illustrated in Figure 
