\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This calculation also provides intuition for the key determinants of the
 optimal tax.
 The denominator is close to one.
 In the numerator, the corrective motive is equal to 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\gamma}(1+\sigma)+e\approx\input{../../Output/Simulations/NumbersForText/gammaBar.tex}(1+\input{../../Output/Simulations/NumbersForText/sigma.tex})+0.85\approx\input{../../Output/Simulations/NumbersForText/corrective.tex}$
\end_inset

