\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{E}\left[\frac{T'(z)}{1-T'(z)}\bar{\zeta}_{z}\bar{s}(z)\bar{\xi}(z)\right]\approx\input{../../Output/Simulations/NumbersForText/fixedinctaxexpec.tex}$
\end_inset

.
