\begin_inset Formula $-Cov\left[g(z),s_{pref}(z)\right]$
\end_inset

.
 This statistic can be computed directly from Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "tab:ManualTable"

\end_inset

, Panel B, where 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{pref}(z)$
\end_inset

