\begin_inset Formula $\bar{s}(z)$
\end_inset

 and consumption predicted from estimated income elasticities, similarly
 to Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:PrefHetVsIncomeEffects"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 In this case, the estimated covariance is 
\begin_inset Formula $Cov\left[g(z),s_{pref}(z)\right]\approx\input{../../Output/Simulations/NumbersForText/covgsPref.tex}$
\end_inset

.
